tag_message: 1.9.7: Updated to sdk tools 25.  Added short description of each calculation method.
Fixed spelling error for "méthode"

1.9.4: maintenance and upgrades:

* Update to the android gradle plugin 2.2.0
* Update to the french revolutionary calendar 1.5.1, which fixes a bug with invalid TimeZones
* Update to google play services 9.6.1
* Update to support library 24.2.1

1.9.3 Maintenance update

* gradle 2.14.1
* gradle plugin 2.1.3
* support 24.2.0
* google play services 9.4.0
Update support library to 23.4.0 and google play services to 9.0.0
1.9.0: Added new calculation method: von Mädler aka the 128-year rule.
Upgraded to french-revolutionary-calendar 1.4.1, to fix a spelling error ("Travail")
Issue #17: Use lowercase with the SEND action
Issue #17: Fix for lookup function.
Added feature to lookup the object of the day (web search)

1.18.1: Rewrote the app in Kotlin.

Also: Use the roman numeral setting in the converter.
1.18.0: Add Basque translation and fix the selection of the default font.
1.17.4: Fixed spelling of Sansculotides, to match the spelling in the [original decree](http://1789-1799.blogspot.fr/2011/12/le-calendrier-republicain-14.html)

1.17.3: Fix Oreo compatibility bugs

* Issue 43: Widget stuck in spinner loading animation on Oreo
* Issue 45: Notification not created on Oreo
1.17.2: Fix crash in new date converter.

1.17.1: New two-way converter.

Replaced the tab layout with single screne that has two date pickers.
1.17.0: Added French to Gregorian date converter.
1.16.0: Replaced the OpenSans font by Roboto.
1.15.2: Fixed spelling error.
1.15.1: Fixed icon color on widget popup
1.15.0: New setting for the notification priority

1.14.0: removed android wear specific code.

* Google play services is no longer used in this project.
* Removed dependency on the support-compat library.
* There is only the default flavor now (previously there were foss and proprietary flavors).
* The system notification, if enabled, is now sent to wearable devices and the phone.
1.13.0: Added setting to display the year in Roman numerals.
1.12.3: Fixed issue 33: Crash when showing notification: honeycomb + ics
1.12.2: Fix typo in French: "Minérale" -> "Minéral"
1.12.1: added search function from the system notification, and updated to google play services 10.0.1

1.11.3: maintenance update:

versionName = "1.11.3"
1.11.1: Specify the app theme explicitly, because the default theme on N is light, which we don't support well.

1.11.0: new date converter screen.

Also minor ui improvements in the about screen1.11.0: new date converter screen.
1.15.1: Fixed icon color on widget popup
